      "description": "Calling all weekend warriors and restoration enthusiasts! This vehicle is ready for a second act and is the perfect project for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a classic back to life. While it's currently in poor condition and will require some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic TLC, it offers a fantastic foundation for a custom build or a valuable source of parts. If you've been looking for an affordable way to start your next big automotive adventure, this is the one for you!",
